in  the  Winthrop  Bowen,  being  Chair.

Thistle  Gaden,  Lawrence  Gourlay,  William  Judson  M.D.,  Lamson,  William
Thomas  Pitt,  James  Edgar  Valentine,  Maj.  Charles  William  Whipple.
